cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper employs sentiment analysis using deep learning on product reviews from an e-commerce website. The use of deep learning and natural language processing techniques suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper involves the analysis of text data, which could also fall under Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The use of neural networks and machine learning techniques also suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves the development of a web service application, which could fall under the sub-category of Computers and Society (cs.CY).
